{"TopicId":201572,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Jet Plane Thingy","CreatedByName":"Nicodo123","CreatedById":210130,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-09T17:54:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Nicodo123","CreatedById":210130,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-09T17:54:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReally wobbly, really hard to control. Just how I like! Maybe you could do a bit better than I can, but all I really care about is that it flies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022D29FEkd.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/D29FEkd.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd here\u0027s the craft file if you wanna mess around or improve it.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Nicodo123/Jet-Plane\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalx.com/Nicodo123/Jet-Plane\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-09T18:23:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice plane. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E As a suggestion, if you angle the front of the engines down slightly, the thrust would align more closely with the mass\u00A0 and the plane would have less of a tendency to lower the nose.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dientus","CreatedById":209823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-09T23:46:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI haven\u0027t downloaded it yet, but just looking at pic, I believe Vanamonde hit the big nail on the head. Great rule of thumb for off-centered thrust.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood job! Keep on going!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-04-09T23:47:01Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2021 11:47  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Dientus\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Espelin .. er spelling\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}